{"tid":1610763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小心暴露行踪：發咗夢嘅，除咗要睇吓社交平台外，仲要睇吓 Google map","createTime":"2019-10-01T19:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T01:27:01.000Z","uid":289493,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3603be44ec55dc923a0b094e011960e42937c530","tid":1610763,"uid":289493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zc9kXhs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzc9kXhs.jpg&h=4b0d050c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來用 Google map 嘅 GPS（分享 location 就會自動問 GPS），不單當時會有機會俾人知道你嘅行踪，Google map仲會保留記錄。<br />\n另外，你睇過邊啲 map，一樣會有記錄。<br />\n如果唔想俾人日後 check 番你嘅行踪，記得要㩒左上角嗰三劃，入去搵 your data in maps， 停用 location history 同 web &amp; app activity，同埋取消記錄。"},{"pid":"727644145e0c3279c91dcd6c1ce6b2d37d2a6c6e","tid":1610763,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jv4XZAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjv4XZAM.jpg&h=1150a5d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【SUCK小隊】 【10.2】 【三罷】 之 【狼來了】  【SUCK塞】【SUCK商場】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1610403/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1610403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手推POST呀!!!"},{"pid":"ef54d9c0efe8e86275eaa335b826f7be896e6c79","tid":1610763,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:15:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ca884a7ef2542c895a4ee2ae9b5e95f9a6d46a3","tid":1610763,"uid":18827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:21:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22ccc71bd5deda845e939f482bfabed520579e26","tid":1610763,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:21:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[10.2行動] 係真香港人就入嚟同我推爆佢！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan